data.eml:eml: Four new free-living marine nematode species (Sabatieria) from the Chukchi Sea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Yang, Peipei, Guo, Yuqing, Chen, Yuzhen, Lin, Rongcheng (2019): Four new free-living marine nematode species (Sabatieria) from the Chukchi Sea.
